# .ignore — patterns for tools built on the `ignore` crate (ripgrep, fd,
# cargo-machete). NOT git; this never affects what git tracks.
#
# `containers/` is a pinned, vendored submodule (`update = none`) — third-party
# code Shannon consumes but does not maintain. Excluding it here keeps
# cargo-machete (pre-commit `cargo-machete` hook) from flagging the submodule's
# own crates as having unused deps, and keeps default rg/fd searches focused on
# Shannon's own tree. Search it explicitly (e.g. `rg --no-ignore -g 'containers/**'`)
# when you need to.
containers/
